sec.p:
Specimens of the genus are found in relatively few collections. We examined 143 specimens from or deposited in the following collections:
Bernice P. Bishop Museum, Honolulu, HI, USA (BPBM),
California Academy of Sciences, San Francisco, CA, USA (CASC);
Canadian Museum of Nature Collection, Ottawa, ON, Canada (CMNC);
M.J. Paulsen Collection, Lincoln, NE, USA (MJPC);
Montana Entomology Collection, Bozeman, MT, USA (MEC); and the
Natural History Museum, London, UK (NHM).
